variables.input:
timeseries timeseries = percentile(dt.frontend.web.page.interaction_to_next_paint, 75),
filter: dt.rum.application.entity in [
  fetch dt.entity.application
  | filter in (entity.name, array($Application))
    | fields id
]
| fieldsAdd value = arrayAvg(timeseries)
| summarize average = avg(value)
| fieldsAdd status = if (average <= 200, 10, 
               else: if (average < 500,  5, 
               else: 0))
| fieldsRemove average

data record( mttr=$mttrHealth,
             avail=$availabilityHealth,
             errors=$errorHealth,
             perf=$performanceHealth,
             resource=$resourceHealth,
             network=$networkHealth,
             database=$databaseHealth,
             cls=$clsHealth,
             lcp=$lcpHealth,
             inp=$inpHealth
            )
| fieldsAdd overallGrade = toDouble(mttr)+toDouble(avail)+toDouble(errors)+toDouble(perf)+toDouble(resource)+toDouble(network)+toDouble(database)+toDouble(cls)+toDouble(lcp)+toDouble(inp)
| fieldsRemove mttr, avail, errors, perf, resource, network, database, cls, inp, lcp
